{"id":229402,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/微博红人作业本-因悼念六四账户遭封（附检讨书/","date":"2012-06-05T01:32:06Z","modified":"2012-06-05T01:32:06Z","title":"微博红人@作业本 因悼念六四账户遭封（附“检讨书”）","content":"<p>在新浪微博拥有200多万粉丝的用户@作业本 因发表纪念六四的微博而导致其账户被封：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-229403\" title=\"zuoyeben2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"130\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben2.png 619w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben2-300x78.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@作业本 曾就自己微博频繁被删之事发表了长微博“检讨书”，后也迅速被删，众多转发也未能幸免：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229404\" title=\"zuoyeben\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/zuoyeben.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"1470\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[10210,8859,8616]}